main_body:
Decision 1999/730/CFSP is hereby amended as follows:
(a) in Article 3(1), the financial reference amount shall be replaced by EUR 1768200;
(b) in the second subparagraph of Article 4, "15 November 2001" shall be replaced by "15 November 2002";
(c) the Annex shall be replaced by the Annex to this Decision.
